,"Blog"],"Blog Search Results":[null,"Zoekresultaten in de blog"],"Blog results":[null,"Resultaten in de Blog"],"Browse free templates and ebooks designed to elevate your sales and marketing skills.":[null,"Bekijk gratis templates en e-books die je kunnen helpen om je verkoop- en marketingvaardigheden aan te scherpen."],"But there are plenty of exciting paths to explore!":[null,"Maar er zijn ook andere interessante dingen!"],"By signing up, you accept our {{Terms of Service}} and {{Privacy Notice}}":[null,"Door te registreren aanvaard je onze {{gebruiksvoorwaarden}} en ons {{privacyverklaring}}"],"CRM":[null,"CRM"],"CRM Comparison":[null,"CRM-vergelijking"],"CRM Pricing Plans | Affordable CRM Software Costs":[null,"CRM abonnementen | Betaalbare CRM-software"],"CRM Video tutorials | Pipedrive Learn":[null,"CRM videotutorials | Pipedrive Learn"],"CRM comparison":[null,"CRM-vergelijking"],"Capture high-quality inbound and outbound leads with LeadBooster, then route them automatically to the right reps for faster follow-ups.":[null,"Verzamel veelbelovende inbound en outbound leads met LeadBooster, en stuur ze vervolgens automatisch door naar de juiste verkopers voor snellere opvolging."],"Carousel":[null,"Carrousel"],"Case studies":[null,"Casestudies"],"Chat live with our award-winning support team during business hours, Monday to Friday.":[null,"Chat live met ons bekroonde ondersteuningsteam op werkdagen tijdens de kantooruren."],"Check newsroom":[null,"Naar de Newsroom"],"Check our quick guides on everything from setting up your pipeline to billing to account settings and more.":[null,"Bekijk onze gidsen over diverse onderwerpen, van het ontwerpen van je pijplijn tot het instellen van je account."],"Check out how companies like yours have smashed their goals in our sales, marketing and CRM case studies on our case study website page.":[null,"Bekijk op onze pagina's met casestudy's hoe andere gelijkaardige bedrijven hun doelstellingen overtreffen op het vlak van verkoop, marketing en CRM. "],"Check status":[null,"Status controleren"],"Check to see if all things Pipedrive are up and running.":[null,"Ga na wat de status is van de systemen van Pipedrive. "],"Choose language":[null,"Kies een taal"],"Close":[null,"Sluiten"],"Close video":[null,""],"Communicate with leads":[null,"Communiceren met leads"],"Compare":[null,"Vergelijken"],"Compare Pipedrive's offering with similar products.":[null,"Vergelijk Pipedrive met gelijkaardige producten."],"Connect Pipedrive to %s+ services and tools with an easy one-click installation.":[null,"Koppel Pipedrive met een klik met meer dan %s diensten en tools."],"Contact managers":[null,"Contactbeheerders"],"Contact support":[null,"Neem contact op met het ondersteuningsteam"],"Continue to Pipedrive":[null,"Verder naar Pipedrive"],"Contracts and e-signatures":[null,"Contracten en elektronische handtekeningen"],"Cookie Notice":[null,"Cookiemelding"],"Cookie Settings":[null,"Cookie-instellingen"],"Copy URL":[null,"URL kopiëren"],"Create custom scoring models tailored to your sales process and enrich company data with fields like industry, size and revenue.":[null,"Stel aangepaste scoremodellen in die zijn afgestemd op je verkoopproces, en vul bedrijfsgegevens aan met informatie zoals de branche, omvang en omzet."],"Custom scoring and company data enrichment":[null,"Aangepaste scores en aangevulde bedrijfsgegevens"],"Department":[null,"Afdeling"],"Designers":[null,"Designers"],"Dev community":[null,"Ontwikkelaars-community"],"Developers":[null,"Ontwikkelaars"],"Developers' Corner":[null,"Voor ontwikkelaars"],"Discover":[null,"Discover"],"Discover Pipedrive's CRM pricing plans. Find the right fit for your business with competitive CRM software costs. Get started today.":[null,"Ontdek de abonnementen van Pipedrive CRM. Kies toonaangevende CRM-softwarekosten die past bij jouw bedrijf. Begin vandaag. "],"Documentation":[null,"Documentatie"],"Downloadable resources":[null,"Downloadbare hulpbronnen"],"Drive results from day one with personalized onboarding.":[null,"Boek snel resultaten dankzij gepersonaliseerde onboarding."],"Drive success from lead to close with full-cycle sales tools":[null,"Tools voor de volledige verkoopcyclus, van leads tot het sluiten van je deal"],"Early careers":[null,"Starters"],"Easily build integrations with our API and reach over 90k companies in the Pipedrive Marketplace.":[null,"Ontwikkel zonder moeite integraties met onze API en bereik meer dan 90.000 bedrijven in de Marktplaats van Pipedrive."],"Easily import data from a spreadsheet or CRM. Integrate with 500+ apps, including Zapier, Zoom and Lemlist.":[null,"Importeer moeiteloos gegevens in Pipedrive met een spreadsheet. Integreer met meer dan 500 apps zoals Zapier, Zoom en Lemlist."],"Easy to customize and organize":[null,"Eenvoudig aan te passen en in te stellen"],"Ebooks":[null,"E-books"],"Email analytics":[null,"E-mailstatistieken"],"Email and communications":[null,"E-mail en communicaties"],"Email builder":[null,"E-mailmaker"],"Email is required":[null,"E-mailadres vereist"],"Email segmentation":[null,"E-mailsegmentering"],"Email should not be blank.":[null,"Het e-mailadres mag niet ontbreken."],"Email software":[null,"E-mailsoftware"],"Enhance performance and save time with AI-driven sales tools.":[null,"Verbeter de prestaties en bespaar tijd met verkooptools die door AI worden aangestuurd."],"Enhanced customization for teams, reports and data fields":[null,"Nog meer aanpassingsmogelijkheden voor teams, rapporten en gegevensvelden"],"Enjoy longer phone support hours and request calls from Monday to Friday, 7:00 am to 11:00 pm (CET/CEST).":[null,"Krijg telefonische ondersteuning op meer tijdstippen en vraag gesprekken aan van maandag tot vrijdag van 7.00 tot 23.00 uur (CET/CEST)."],"Enter your email address below to receive your free download link.":[null,"Vul hieronder je e-mailadres in om de link naar de gratis download te ontvangen."],"Enter your work email":[null,"Vul je zakelijke e-mailadres in"],"Explore onboarding support":[null,"Ondersteuning voor onboarding bekijken"],"Extended phone support":[null,"Uitgebreide telefonische ondersteuning"],"Features":[null,"Functies"],"Features and Products":[null,"Functies en Producten"],"Filters":[null,""],"Find careers at Pipedrive.":[null,"Kom bij Pipedrive werken."],"Find setup guides, FAQs and tutorials":[null,"Bekijk gidsen, FAQ's en tutorials"],"Follow Pipedrive on Instagram":[null,""],"Follow Pipedrive on X":[null,""],"Fortified account security with rules and alerts":[null,"Regels en meldingen voor nog betere accountbeveiliging"],"Free 14-day trial. No commitment – you can make changes anytime.":[null,"Gratis proefabonnement van 14 dagen. Zonder verplichtingen - je kunt op elk gewenst moment wijzigingen aanbrengen."],"Free 14-day trial. No credit card required.":[null,"Gratis proefperiode van 14 dagen. Geen creditcard vereist."],"Free Excel sales dashboards":[null,"Gratis Excel sales-dashboards"],"Full access. No credit card required.":[null,"Volledige toegang. Geen creditcard vereist."],"Full email sync with tracking":[null,"Volledige e-mailsynchronisatie en traceren van e-mail"],"Fully sync Gmail, Outlook or your company email. Send bulk emails and track opens and link clicks in real time.":[null,"Synchroniseer alles met Gmail, Outlook of je eigen zakelijke e-mailoplossing. Verzend e-mails in bulk en volg in real time op wie ze opent en op je links klikt."],"Generate reports using text input or choose from pre-written prompts":[null,"Genereer rapporten via een tekstinvoer, of gebruik vooraf opgestelde prompts"],"Get expert advice from sales pros, step-by-step guides.":[null,"Krijg advies van verkoopexperts en raadpleeg stappenplannen."],"Get help":[null,"Hulp vragen"],"Get help with any questions or issues you have.":[null,"Krijg antwoorden op al je vragen over Pipedrive."],"Get helpful tips, product updates and exclusive offers via email":[null,"Ontvang tips, updates en exclusieve aanbiedingen via e-mail"],"Get our newsletter":[null,"Bestel je nieuwsbrief"],"Get started with Pipedrive":[null,"Aan de slag met Pipedrive"],"Google":[null,"Google"],"Growth":[null,"Growth"],"Growth plan +":[null,"Alles in Growth, plus"],"Guide to activity-based sales":[null,"Gids naar op activiteit gebaseerde verkopen"],"Help":[null,"Hulp"],"Help Center":[null,"Helpcentrum"],"Help and Info":[null,"Hulp en Informatie"],"How to build a sales pipeline":[null,"Hoe je een salespijplijn maakt"],"HubSpot":[null,"HubSpot"],"If you haven't signed up with this email, please {{contact our support}}":[null,"Als je je niet hebt aangemeld met dit e-mailadres, neem dan contact op met het {{ondersteuningsteam}}"],"Improve data quality with required and pipeline-specific fields, automate deal calculations with formula fields and build reports with custom data. Control visibility and access with flexible permissions at group and individual levels.":[null,"Zorg voor betere gegevens via verplichte en pijplijnspecifieke velden, automatiseer dealberekeningen met formulevelden, en stel rapporten op met aangepaste gegevens. Beheer de zichtbaarheid en toegang met flexibele machtigingen voor groepen en personen."],"Industries":[null,"Branches"],"Industries and Roles":[null,"Branches en Rollen"],"Insights and reports":[null,"Inzichten en rapporten"],"Integrations":[null,"Integraties"],"Jobs":[null,"Opdrachten"],"Join Pipedrive's channel program designed to power you with resources and tools for success.":[null,"Neem deel aan het partnerprogramma van Pipedrive en ontvang hulpbronnen en tools waarmee je echt aan de slag kunt."],"Join a community of sales professionals from %s+ companies worldwide, and receive sales tips and Pipedrive updates once a week.":[null,"Sluit je aan bij een wereldwijde community met salesprofessionals van meer dan %s bedrijven over de hele wereld, en ontvang wekelijks verkooptips en updates van Pipedrive."],"Join the 2-week email {{course}} and start selling more":[null,"Doe mee met de 2-weekse {{e-mailcursus}} en verkoop nog meer"],"Keep up to date with Pipedrive in the media.":[null,"Blijf op de hoogte van mediabelangstelling rond Pipedrive."],"Key features":[null,"Belangrijkste functies"],"Knowledge Base":[null,"Kennisdatabase"],"Knowledge Base results":[null,"Resultaten in de Kennisdatabase"],"Knowledge base":[null,"Kennisdatabase"],"Latest articles":[null,"Meest recente artikels"],"Lead generation and routing":[null,"Genereren en doorsturen van leads"],"Lead management":[null,"Leadbeheer"],"Lead managers":[null,"Leadmanagers"],"Lead, calendar and pipeline management":[null,"Beheer van leads, agenda's en pijplijnen"],"Learn":[null,"Leren"],"Learn about Pipedrive and how we became the first CRM made by salespeople for salespeople.":[null,"Kom meer te weten over Pipedrive - de eerste CRM gemaakt door verkopers, voor verkopers."],"Learn how Pipedrive helps different roles across the organization improve their performance.":[null,"Bekijk hoe Pipedrive mensen met diverse rollen binnen een organisatie helpt om hun prestaties te verbeteren."],"Learn how Pipedrive systematically increases revenue for all types of industries.":[null,"Ontdek hoe Pipedrive systematisch de omzet verhoogt voor bedrijven in allerlei branches."],"Learn more about careers":[null,"Meer over vacatures"],"Learn more about us":[null,"Meer over ons"],"Learn the basics of Pipedrive: Watch the free course":[null,"Hoe Pipedrive werkt: bekijk de gratis cursus"],"Let customers pick a meeting time that works for you both, and view a full history of interactions in the contacts timeline.":[null,"Laat je klanten een tijd kiezen die voor jullie beiden geschikt is, en bekijk een volledige geschiedenis van interacties met een contactpersoon in een tijdlijn."],"Lite":[null,"Lite"],"Lite plan +":[null,"Alles in Lite, plus"],"Live chat support":[null,"Ondersteuning via live chat"],"Location":[null,"Locatie"],"Log in":[null,"Aanmelden"],"Log out":[null,"Afmelden"],"Manage contracts